{"tid":1126323,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"原來數碼暴龍小說有講四聖獸對黑暗四天王嘅下場","createTime":"2019-04-26T10:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T13:54:49.000Z","uid":64694,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8ac35b96ee5d1256a2c61319da77601fee5b0cf7","tid":1126323,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:07:40.000Z","msg":"唔知係同人小說定官方小說啦<br />\n<br />\n鋼鐵海龍獸 vs 青龍獸<br />\n木偶獸 vs 玄武獸<br />\n機械邪龍獸 vs 白虎獸<br />\n小丑皇 vs 朱雀獸<br />\n<br />\n鋼鐵海龍獸打贏咗青龍獸<br />\n木偶獸用個錘仔一嘢敲落去玄武獸度，玄武獸就再起唔到身了<br />\n機械邪龍獸同白虎獸大戰八日八夜，雖然打平，但最後白虎獸都難免被封印<br />\n最後小丑皇，小丑皇實在太強，一嘢踩咗落去朱雀獸度，踩住朱雀獸喺地吓，直接輸掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfa641ee539034236d80919a8661c46c1929017","tid":1126323,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:09:19.000Z","msg":"邊度睇返嚟"},{"pid":"9dfffa14b806e6e80123e275bc1b4c6837feb92d","tid":1126323,"uid":2994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:09:54.000Z","msg":"咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"e366df6261e48cbfae6be563e0254e9149bf4f63","tid":1126323,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dfffa14b806e6e80123e275bc1b4c6837feb92d","tid":1126323,"uid":2994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:09:54.000Z","msg":"咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:12:29.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔係勁"},{"pid":"6b1eef4492295338e5cade7ef91b68a695d22572","tid":1126323,"uid":38383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:14:12.000Z","msg":"木偶獸同小丑皇合理 但唔信青龍獸打唔鋼鐵海龍獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2fd24fba5fc74f534d426a78bd3be68e04d1b49","tid":1126323,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:17:25.000Z","msg":"所以係戰暴&gt;鋼鐵海龍&gt;青龍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 